806
01:23:43,485 --> 01:23:45,112
But l couldn't stop them

807
01:23:52,293 --> 01:23:56,855
l told myself l would soon be home

808
01:23:59,100 --> 01:24:00,533
They wouldn't let me go

809
01:24:03,304 --> 01:24:06,865
