812
01:24:19,721 --> 01:24:20,881
l lost everything

813
01:24:56,291 --> 01:24:57,121
Vennila!

814
01:24:59,961 --> 01:25:00,985
Watch out

815
01:25:07,368 --> 01:25:09,461
Pull it

816
