828
01:26:59,013 --> 01:27:02,949
l'll tell you one thing
A stiff drink will...

829
01:27:03,451 --> 01:27:06,284
-Hurry up
-Lift him. -Ok sir

830
01:27:08,323 --> 01:27:10,553
He was there for a few hours

831
01:27:10,658 --> 01:27:12,148
