832
01:27:12,260 --> 01:27:15,696
-Enough!
-l say ''enough'' too

833
01:27:16,331 --> 01:27:18,094
-Take him to camp..
-When big convoys like ours advance,

834
01:27:18,199 --> 01:27:20,360
..everyone knows.
Even the ants

835
01:27:21,002 --> 01:27:24,699
