and make us bald

836
01:27:24,939 --> 01:27:26,429
Any bright ideas?

837
01:27:27,609 --> 01:27:30,976
One, sir. l need your permission
That's enough

838
01:27:48,896 --> 01:27:49,863
Give me strength

839
01:27:51,966 --> 01:27:53,729
Don't take my anger away

840
01:27:55,970 --> 01:27:57,528
Anger gives me the will to live

841
01:28:00,308 --> 01:28:02,208
