843
01:28:05,179 --> 01:28:07,204
Don't show bad people in good light

844
01:28:08,516 --> 01:28:09,744
Nor show them as truthful

845
01:28:19,661 --> 01:28:21,151
Give me the courage to fight

846
01:28:22,397 --> 01:28:23,830
My anger cannot lessen

847
01:28:24,932 --> 01:28:26,229
Can't you do that much for me?

848
01:28:42,884 --> 01:28:45,250
