-We'll throw chilli
in their eyes and escape -Oh God!

905
01:33:24,699 --> 01:33:27,668
Don't hurt him.
You already have me captive

906
01:33:28,102 --> 01:33:30,002
l am going to slay
him like a goat

907
01:33:30,104 --> 01:33:31,332
Will you throw chilli at us?

908
01:33:47,388 --> 01:33:50,482
Your death-knell too
l hear many sounds

909
01:33:50,658 --> 01:33:53,024
The inspector's convoy is
heading this way

910
01:33:53,127 --> 01:33:55,493
Watch out

911
01:33:56,864 --> 01:33:59,094
l may be from the lnspector's party

912
01:33:59,667 --> 01:34:01,498
