for you. Even die

915
01:34:09,543 --> 01:34:10,510
Am l wrong?

916
01:34:12,480 --> 01:34:15,040
They will do
You've done so much for them

917
01:34:16,217 --> 01:34:21,587
But l ask you, why would you
want to risk their lives?

918
01:34:23,424 --> 01:34:25,255
You're the only one who'll die

919
01:34:25,359 --> 01:34:27,190
You will die with in a minute..

920
01:34:28,095 --> 01:34:31,724
Send madam back with me.
Stop this quarrel

921
01:34:31,832 --> 01:34:33,197
We'll drop all charges

922
01:34:34,235 --> 01:34:36,999
-What if we don't send her back?
-Go man

923
01:34:37,104 --> 01:34:39,538
He hears the whole story.
Still gets it back to front

924
01:34:39,640 --> 01:34:43,076
Need l answer?
The end of the world

925
01:34:43,177 --> 01:34:44,201
All over and done with

926
01:34:44,378 --> 01:34:46,073
