-Are you scared of dying?
-Why should we have fear?

932
01:35:00,795 --> 01:35:05,357
-Anyone scared?
-Why are you asking like that?

933
01:35:05,466 --> 01:35:08,902
No one seems scared.
So now what?

934
01:35:09,737 --> 01:35:13,036
Throw stones at a dog.
lt will bark and then bite you

935
01:35:13,474 --> 01:35:16,637
Force a tree branch down and let go

936
01:35:16,744 --> 01:35:17,711
lt will spring up with greater might

937
01:35:18,946 --> 01:35:20,436
