939
01:35:22,817 --> 01:35:24,910
They hit us.
We hit back

940
01:35:25,352 --> 01:35:28,185
They caned us.
We did the same

941
01:35:28,556 --> 01:35:30,524
The bastards point guns at us now

942
01:35:33,627 --> 01:35:37,654
We'll snap your necks. Understand?

943
01:35:38,532 --> 01:35:42,628
Veera, l won't leave
this place without madam

944
01:35:47,007 --> 01:35:49,032
Who said you were leaving? Eh?

945
01:35:50,411 --> 01:35:53,244
Brother! His end is near

946
