Let me go with the forest guard

973
01:37:15,029 --> 01:37:15,859
Make him see sense

974
01:37:23,304 --> 01:37:28,469
lt is mistake going
to the police

975
01:37:28,576 --> 01:37:31,875
lt's mistake.
Sending him alone is a mistake

976
01:37:31,979 --> 01:37:33,412
l'll go with him

977
01:37:35,049 --> 01:37:35,947
l'll go with him

978
01:37:36,050 --> 01:37:38,348
