l came here to talk peace

1011
01:40:20,414 --> 01:40:21,779
l want peace too

1012
01:40:25,886 --> 01:40:28,787
No more bad blood

1013
01:40:32,159 --> 01:40:33,456
Send Ragini back

1014
01:40:37,297 --> 01:40:38,730
Veera will come to no harm

1015
01:40:46,507 --> 01:40:48,270
Come out when you want to talk

1016
01:40:52,379 --> 01:40:53,471
l'll be waiting in my tent

