and dethrone you''

1031
01:45:13,140 --> 01:45:15,165
Hemanth, careful

1032
01:45:40,767 --> 01:45:43,235
Keep coming and you'll die

1033
01:45:54,181 --> 01:45:56,240
A round of applause!

1034
01:45:56,650 --> 01:46:03,249
He isn't running.
